<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>CampWeekdayTask7</title>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <%= csp_meta_tag %>

    <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
    <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="jumbotron text-center" style="margin-bottom:0">
      <h1>ジョナサンで作成した論文アプリ</h1>
      <p>論文をたくさん読めばきっといことがあります。知識は力なり</p>
    </div>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-sm bg-dark navbar-dark">
      <%= link_to 'Articles', articles_path, class: 'navbar-brand' %>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse">
          <ul class="navbar-nav">
            <li class="nav-item">
              <%= link_to 'New posts', new_article_path, class: "nav-link" %>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-9 my-5 pr-3 mr-5">
          <%= yield %>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-1 bg-dark ml-3">
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-2">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>